[A spacing policy. name, bodyLeading, headingLeading, captionLeading, codeLeading, baselineGridUnit, and paragraphSpacing are required.]
<SpacingPolicy id=urn:paperhat:example:spacing-policy:example baselineGridUnit="12pt" bodyLeading="1.5" captionLeading="1.3" codeLeading="1.4" headingLeading="1.2" name="Spacing Policy Name" paragraphSpacing="12pt" />

[A paragraph policy. name, defaultAlignment, headingAlignment, minimumBeforeBreak, minimumAfterBreak, maximumConsecutiveHyphens, minimumWidowLines, and minimumOrphanLines are required.]
<ParagraphPolicy id=urn:paperhat:example:paragraph-policy:example defaultAlignment=$Left headingAlignment=$Left maximumConsecutiveHyphens=3 minimumAfterBreak=2 minimumBeforeBreak=2 minimumOrphanLines=2 minimumWidowLines=2 name="Paragraph Policy Name" />

[A typography accessibility policy. name, minimumBodySize, minimumCaptionSize, minimumLeadingRatio, minimumMeasureCharacters, and maximumMeasureCharacters are required.]
<TypographyAccessibilityPolicy id=urn:paperhat:example:typography-accessibility-policy:example maximumMeasureCharacters=75 minimumBodySize="16pt" minimumCaptionSize="12pt" minimumLeadingRatio="1.5" minimumMeasureCharacters=45 name="Typography Accessibility Policy Name" />
